flowchart TD
    %% Greenfield Flow — new repo, install kit, ship first feature

    NEW[(New / near-empty repo)] --> BOOT["install.sh<br/>Seed skills, rules, and memories"]:::green
    BOOT --> INIT["starter-init (Phase B)<br/>Greenfield Mode"]:::green

    INIT --> AGENTS["Configure AGENTS.md router<br/>Verify entrypoint file is present"]:::step
    INIT --> MEMSEED["Seed memories/repo/<br/>core-policies.md,<br/>and project-knowledge-base.md"]:::step
    INIT --> TMPL["Pre-fill templates<br/>core-zero/project/*.md<br/>and core-zero/project/architecture.md"]:::step
    INIT --> BASE["Harness Readiness Check<br/>Run build and baseline tests"]:::step

    AGENTS --> SPEC
    MEMSEED --> SPEC
    TMPL --> SPEC
    BASE --> SPEC["spec-requirements<br/>(grilling waves + spec.md)"]:::green

    SPEC --> PLAN["spec-plan<br/>(plan.md + tasks.md)"]:::green
    PLAN --> IMPL["spec-implement<br/>(one task at a time + proof)"]:::step
    IMPL --> VERIFY["harness-verify<br/>(review.md + testing-scenarios.md)"]:::gate

    VERIFY -- gate fail --> IMPL
    VERIFY -- pass --> SYNC["Post-Ship Sync<br/>(context-memory sweep)"]:::gate
    SYNC --> ENDS["context-session END<br/>(handoff.md + session-extracts.md)"]:::step
    ENDS --> DONE([First feature shipped<br/>KB seeded for next feature]):::terminal

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef green fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
    classDef step fill:#fff,stroke:#d0d7de,color:#0d0d0d
    classDef gate fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff

    class NEW,DONE terminal
